OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,FThe Chief Constable of Greater
OL,7,FManchester Police says the force was
OL,8,F"a three (out of 10) at best" before
OL,9,Fhe arrived saying he "anticipated that
OL,10,Fit would be pretty grim - and it was".
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Granada Reports Sir
OL,13,FStephen Watson, who took up the role
OL,14,Fin May 2021, said the struggles were
OL,15,Flargely down to a "failure of
OL,16,Fleadership" at the time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/19
