OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,FBut he says he is proud of the
OL,7,Fimprovements it has made since it was
OL,8,Fput into special measures in 2020,
OL,9,Fwith the force ranked the most
OL,10,Fimproved in the country in 2023.
OL,12,FThe force chief recently received a
OL,13,Fknighthood for his extensive
OL,14,Fcommitment to policing.
OL,16,FOn GMP's struggles he said: "Greater
OL,17,FManchester was going through a bad
OL,18,Fpatch, there's no denying it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
