OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1770125981
OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,F"It was officially going through a bad
OL,7,Fpatch in the sense that His Majesty's
OL,8,FInspectorate had placed the force into
OL,9,Fspecial measures."
OL,11,F"The frank fact of the moment was that
OL,12,Fat that point, we were just not doing
OL,13,Fany of the basics very well," he added.
OL,15,F"We weren't picking up the phone, we
OL,16,Fweren't responding to people, we
OL,17,Fweren't making accurate records."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/19
