OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,FSir Stephen believed that the problem
OL,7,Fat the time was the "strategic
OL,8,Farchitecture" of the force, despite
OL,9,Fhaving great faith in GMP as a whole.
OL,11,F"It was a failure of leadership," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"It was a failure to give expression
OL,15,Fto what was in the hearts and minds of
OL,16,Four people because, it seems to me, a
OL,17,Fself-evident truth that if you don't
OL,18,Fcreate the circumstances in which good
OL,19,Fpeople can perform, then they're not
OL,20,Fgoing to perform.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
