OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1770125981
OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,F"But it's not always their fault, it
OL,7,Fis the fault generally of senior
OL,8,Fleadership.
OL,10,F"I'm very proud of my Chief Officer
OL,11,Fteam and at all levels of leadership
OL,12,Fthroughout the organisation, that in
OL,13,Fterms of the discharge of the
OL,14,Fleadership function, we have created a
OL,15,Fclimate within which our people can
OL,16,Fthrive."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/19
