OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police responded to
OL,7,F92.8% of 999 calls within 10 seconds
OL,8,Fin December 2025, compared to just
OL,9,F45.8% in May 2021. The force has the
OL,10,Ffourth highest 999 volume in the UK.
OL,12,FSpeaking about what he believed he
OL,13,Fneeded to do on his arrival, Sir
OL,14,FStephen said the force was not
OL,15,Fdelivering on "basic service provision
OL,16,Fto the public".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/19
