OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1770125981
OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,F"Of course you need to turn up and you
OL,7,Fneed to actually take your coat off
OL,8,Fand get your sleeves rolled up to
OL,9,Ffully appreciate how things were, but
OL,10,Fcandidly, I anticipated that it would
OL,11,Fbe pretty grim and it was," he said.
OL,13,F"It was simply not performing, and it
OL,14,Fwasn't performing across all of those
OL,15,Fmeasures that might describe basic
OL,16,Fservice provision to the public.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
