OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1770125981
OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,F"That is why our focus, when we talk
OL,7,Fabout a back to basics approach,
OL,8,Fessentially, what that means is just
OL,9,Fpeel it back to what it is the public
OL,10,Fare expecting us to do and what might
OL,11,Fthey reasonably expect of us."
OL,13,FHe now believes that his force is
OL,14,Fdoing better work by reducing risk and
OL,15,Fharm and increasing confidence.
OL,17,FSir Stephen said: "There was a school
OL,18,Fof thought that that we're just too
OL,19,Fbusy, demand is just too high, we
OL,20,Fdon't have enough money, we don't have
OL,21,Fenough people.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
