OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,F"But the reality is, so much of what
OL,7,Fwas coming through the doors was a
OL,8,Fsymptom of our failure to grip stuff
OL,9,Fin the first place.
OL,11,F"My people still work very hard, but
OL,12,Fwhereas we were busy being busy badly,
OL,13,Fthey are now busy being professional
OL,14,Fand effective, and they are reducing
OL,15,Fcrime, they are reducing threat, risk
OL,16,Fand harm, and they are increasing
OL,17,Fconfidence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/19
