OL,6,F"People who are intent on doing harm
OL,7,Fto the people whom we serve are now
OL,8,Fvery, very firmly on the back foot,
OL,9,Fand that's where we intend to keep
OL,10,Fthem."
OL,12,FWho is Sir Stephen Watson?
OL,14,FSir Stephen began his career as a
OL,15,Fconstable with Lancashire Police in
OL,16,F1988 and has also served with
OL,17,FMerseyside Police, the Metropolitan
OL,18,FPolice and Durham Constabulary.
