OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,FHe was appointed as Chief Constable of
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) in May
OL,8,F2021 after the previous chief
OL,9,Fconstable resigned with the force in
OL,10,Fspecial measures.
OL,12,FSince 2021, under Sir Stephen's
OL,13,Fleadership, the force have seen one of
OL,14,Fthe most rapid and wide-ranging
OL,15,Ftransformations which has seen GMP go
OL,16,Ffrom the worst-performing force to one
OL,17,Fof the best.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/19
