OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,FSpeaking about the proposed
OL,7,FHillsborough Law, after campaigners
OL,8,Fwithdrew their support for the
OL,9,Fproposed law over fears of whether it
OL,10,Fwould fully apply to security
OL,11,Fservices, Sir Stephen, who served as
OL,12,FChief Constable of South Yorkshire
OL,13,FPolice from 2016 to 2021, says he
OL,14,Fsupported the law in full.
OL,16,F"A big part, a big part of what the
OL,17,Ffamilies have campaigned for for many
OL,18,Fyears is a duty of candour, because
OL,19,Fwho can deny that the events of
OL,20,FHillsborough were dreadful in and of
OL,21,Fthemselves," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1770125981
OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,F"But they must have been made worse by
OL,7,Fpeople seeking to cover their tracks,
OL,8,Fgive a partial account, give an
OL,9,Faccount which only answers very
OL,10,Fspecifically the question that's put,
OL,11,Fdoesn't perhaps answer other things
OL,12,Fthat aren't put.
OL,14,F"That taken together, I think tainted
OL,15,Fwhat was already a dreadful set of
OL,16,Fcircumstances and made people believe
OL,17,Fthat not only were we incompetent, but
OL,18,Fwe were also dishonest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
