CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1770125981
OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,F"And that it seems to me is something
OL,7,Fthat we absolutely need to move away
OL,8,Ffrom, and that is why a duty of
OL,9,Fcandour is important and it is why I
OL,10,Fsupport it."
OL,12,FAfter an inquiry into the Manchester
OL,13,FArena bombing in 2017, Greater
OL,14,FManchester Police admitted they
OL,15,F"failed to plan effectively" and that
OL,16,Ftheir actions were "substantially
OL,17,Finadequate".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
