OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,FSir John Saunders' report into the
OL,7,Femergency services found that GMP did
OL,8,Fnot lead the response in accordance
OL,9,Fwith guidance, including a failure by
OL,10,Fthe Force Duty Officer to inform other
OL,11,Femergency services of his declaration
OL,12,Fof Operation Plato - the code name for
OL,13,Fthe pre-planned emergency response to
OL,14,Fa marauding terrorist.
OL,16,FSpeaking about the inquiry findings,
OL,17,FSir Stephen said: "We did not respond
OL,18,Fas we ought to have done. We let
OL,19,Fpeople down, we let families down, and
OL,20,Fwe made a bad situation worse, and we
OL,21,Fhave learned from it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
