CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1770125981
OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,F"And as I think people can appreciate,
OL,7,Fwhen we have had, sadly, to reactivate
OL,8,Fan emergency response to a dreadful
OL,9,Fexample, such as the unforgivable
OL,10,Fattack on the Heaton Park synagogue,
OL,11,Fyou can see how that learning is baked
OL,12,Finto the GMP of today, and you can see
OL,13,Fhow our response was first class."
OL,15,FOverall, the Chief Constable says the
OL,16,Fforce now has a "professional" and
OL,17,F"focused" environment and a team he is
OL,18,Fproud of.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/19
