OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,FHe said: "Sometimes we mess things up,
OL,7,Fand when we do, we'll put our hands
OL,8,Fup, we'll redouble our efforts, and
OL,9,Fwe'll try again.
OL,11,F"For the most part, we don't mess
OL,12,Fstuff up. For the most part, we're
OL,13,Fdoing really well. Our people are
OL,14,Fdoing brilliantly in a very difficult
OL,15,Foperating environment, very often
OL,16,Funder great pressure, and they come
OL,17,Fthrough day in and day out doing
OL,18,Freally, really good work."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/19
