OL,3,CChief Constable blames 'failure of
OL,4,Cleadership' for force's struggles
OL,6,F"But I am very, very clear that this
OL,7,Fis an honour that really reflects the
OL,8,Fwork of the many thousands of men and
OL,9,Fwomen that I have worked with up and
OL,10,Fdown the country in British policing
OL,11,Fmore generally, and latterly, of
OL,12,Fcourse, and brilliantly with the men
OL,13,Fand women of Greater Manchester
OL,14,FPolice."
